Trailers & Promos: Mohit Sajnaney 
Release Date: 14 August 2025 

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji.

snippet.title: FRUIT MIXER | Colorful Healthy Fruits Mixed Recipe | Summer Health Fruit Recipe Making in Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we made a colorful and healthy fruit mixer using fresh fruits. We included apples, oranges, watermelon, strawberries, kiwis, mangoes, papayas, jackfruit, and more, along with soaked almond gum, basil seeds, and pure honey for added taste and health benefits.

The video beautifully cuts and shows all the fruits, making it refreshing and satisfying to watch. This natural recipe is perfect for all seasons, especially summer, and is a great healthy fruit recipe for kids.

hi.title: फल मिक्सर | रंग-बिरंगे स्वस्थ फल मिश्रित रेसिपी | गांव में गर्मियों में स्वास्थ्यवर्धक फल रेसिपी ...
hi.description:
आज हमारे गांव में, हमने ताजे फलों का उपयोग करके एक रंगीन और स्वस्थ फल मिक्सर बनाया। हमने सेब, संतरे, तरबूज, स्ट्रॉबेरी, कीवी, आम, पपीता, कटहल, और बहुत कुछ शामिल किया, साथ ही स्वाद और स्वास्थ्य लाभ के लिए भिगोए हुए बादाम गोंद, तुलसी के बीज और शुद्ध शहद भी मिलाया।

वीडियो में सभी फलों को खूबसूरती से काटा और दिखाया गया है, जिससे इसे देखना ताज़ा और संतोषजनक लगता है। यह प्राकृतिक नुस्खा सभी मौसमों, खासकर गर्मियों के लिए एकदम सही है, और बच्चों के लिए एक बढ़िया स्वस्थ फल नुस्खा है।

id.title: FRUIT MIXER | Resep Campuran Buah Sehat Berwarna-warni | Resep Buah Sehat Musim Panas yang Dibuat...
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami membuat campuran buah yang berwarna-warni dan sehat menggunakan buah-buahan segar. Kami memasukkan apel, jeruk, semangka, stroberi, kiwi, mangga, pepaya, nangka, dan banyak lagi, bersama dengan getah almond yang direndam, biji kemangi, dan madu murni untuk menambah rasa dan manfaat kesehatan.

Video ini memotong dan menunjukkan semua buah dengan indah, sehingga menyegarkan dan memuaskan untuk ditonton. Resep alami ini cocok untuk semua musim, terutama musim panas, dan merupakan resep buah sehat yang bagus untuk anak-anak.

it.title: Mix di frutta | Ricetta per un mix di frutta sana e colorata | Ricetta per un mix di frutta sana ...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo preparato un frullato di frutta colorato e sano usando frutta fresca. Abbiamo aggiunto mele, arance, anguria, fragole, kiwi, mango, papaya, jackfruit e altro ancora, insieme a gomma di mandorle in ammollo, semi di basilico e miele puro per un gusto ancora più intenso e benefici per la salute.

Il video mostra e taglia splendidamente tutti i frutti, rendendolo rinfrescante e appagante da guardare. Questa ricetta naturale è perfetta per tutte le stagioni, soprattutto d'estate, ed è un'ottima ricetta di frutta sana per i bambini.

de-DE.title: FRUCHTMIXER | Rezept für bunte, gesunde Früchte | Sommerliches, gesundes Obstrezept im Dorf zuber...
de-DE.description:
Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf einen farbenfrohen und gesunden Fruchtmixer mit frischen Früchten zubereitet. Wir haben Äpfel, Orangen, Wassermelonen, Erdbeeren, Kiwis, Mangos, Papayas, Jackfrüchte und mehr verwendet, zusammen mit eingeweichtem Mandelkernmehl, Basilikumsamen und reinem Honig für zusätzlichen Geschmack und gesunde Vorteile.

Das Video zeigt alle Früchte mit schönen Schnitten und ist erfrischend und unterhaltsam anzusehen. Dieses natürliche Rezept eignet sich perfekt für jede Jahreszeit, besonders für den Sommer, und ist ein tolles, gesundes Obstrezept für Kinder.

fr-FR.title: MÉLANGEUR DE FRUITS | Recette de mélange de fruits sains et colorés | Recette de fruits sains pou...
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons préparé un mixeur de fruits coloré et sain avec des fruits frais. Nous avons utilisé des pommes, des oranges, de la pastèque, des fraises, des kiwis, des mangues, des papayes, du jacquier et bien d'autres ingrédients, ainsi que de la gomme d'amande imbibée, des graines de basilic et du miel pur pour plus de goût et de bienfaits pour la santé.

La vidéo présente tous les fruits avec élégance, ce qui la rend rafraîchissante et agréable à regarder. Cette recette naturelle est parfaite en toutes saisons, surtout en été, et constitue une excellente recette de fruits saine pour les enfants.

ja.title: フルーツミキサー | カラフルでヘルシーなフルーツミックスレシピ | 村で作る夏のヘルシーフルーツレシピ
ja.description:
今日は村で、新鮮なフルーツを使ってカラフルでヘルシーなフルーツミキサーを作りました。リンゴ、オレンジ、スイカ、イチゴ、キウイ、マンゴー、パパイヤ、ジャックフルーツなど、様々なフルーツに加え、風味と健康効果を高めるために、アーモンドガム、バジルシード、そして純粋なハチミツを加えました。

この動画では、様々なフルーツが美しくカットされ、その姿が映し出されているので、見ているだけで爽快で満足感があります。このナチュラルなレシピは、特に夏など、どの季節にもぴったりで、お子様にもぴったりのヘルシーなフルーツレシピです。

pt-BR.title: MIXER DE FRUTAS | Receita de Frutas Coloridas e Saudáveis ​​| Receita de Frutas Saudáveis ​​para ...
pt-BR.description:
Hoje, em nossa aldeia, fizemos uma mistura de frutas colorida e saudável usando frutas frescas. Incluímos maçãs, laranjas, melancia, morangos, kiwis, mangas, mamões, jacas e muito mais, além de goma de amêndoa demolhada, sementes de manjericão e mel puro para adicionar sabor e benefícios à saúde.

O vídeo corta e mostra todas as frutas com perfeição, tornando-o refrescante e prazeroso de assistir. Esta receita natural é perfeita para todas as estações, especialmente o verão, e é uma ótima receita de frutas saudáveis ​​para crianças.

es-US.title: MEZCLADOR DE FRUTAS | Receta de frutas variadas, coloridas y saludables | Receta de frutas saluda...
es-US.description:
Hoy en nuestro pueblo, preparamos una colorida y saludable mezcla de frutas frescas. Incluimos manzanas, naranjas, sandía, fresas, kiwis, mangos, papayas, yaca y más, además de goma de almendras remojada, semillas de albahaca y miel pura para darle más sabor y beneficios para la salud.

El video muestra todas las frutas con una cuidada selección, lo que lo hace refrescante y satisfactorio. Esta receta natural es perfecta para todas las estaciones, especialmente el verano, y es una excelente receta de frutas saludables para niños.

snippet.title: Bhide ने फेंका Dr. Hathi के ऊपर बाल्टी भरके पानी | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Scenes
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Bhide is out in his living room, relaxing as he reads the newspaper. But soon his peace gets disrupted by Tapu Sena's constant noise and he tells them to keep quiet! Find out more by watching the episode.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 597
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025  #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #comedyscene #tmkocbestcomedy 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Comedy Scenes' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cS8wi0cuF6h1ZN4wQuXjH2m

snippet.title: Jurassic World Rebirth | Official Tamil Trailer 2
snippet.description:
மிக மோசமான டைனோசர்கள் இங்கே விடப்பட்டன. ஜுராசிக் வேர்ல்ட் ரீபர்த்தின் இறுதி ட்ரைலரை காணுங்கள்.   ஜூலை 4, தியேட்டர்களில் மட்டும்.  ஆங்கிலம், ஹிந்தி, தமிழ் மற்றும் தெலுங்கு ஆகிய மொழிகளில் வெளியாகிறது.

Follow us on Facebook at   / universalpicturesindia  
Find us on Instagram at   / universalpicturesindia  
Follow us on Twitter at https://x.com/UniversalIND 

Genre:​​Epic Action-Adventure
Cast: Scarlett Johansson, Mahershala Ali, Jonathan Bailey, Rupert Friend, Manuel Garcia-Rulfo, Luna Blaise, David Iacono, Audrina Miranda, Philippine Velge, Bechir Sylvain, Ed Skrein
Director: Gareth Edwards
Screenplay by: David Koepp based on characters created by Michael Crichton
Producers: Frank Marshall, Patrick Crowley
Executive Producers: Steven Spielberg, Denis L. Stewart, Jim Spencer

A new era is born.

Next summer, three years after the Jurassic World trilogy concluded with each film surpassing $1 billion at the global box office, the enduring Jurassic series evolves in an ingenious new direction with Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Anchored by iconic action superstar Scarlett Johansson, breakthrough talent Jonathan Bailey and two-time Oscar® winner Mahershala Ali, this action-packed new chapter sees an intrepid team racing to secure DNA samples from the three most colossal creatures across land, sea and air. Also starring acclaimed international stars Rupert Friend and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo, the film is directed by dynamic visualist Gareth Edwards (Rogue One: A Star Wars Story) from a script by original Jurassic Park screenwriter David Koepp. 

Five years after the events of Jurassic World Dominion, the planet’s ecology has proven largely inhospitable to dinosaurs. Those remaining exist in isolated equatorial environments with climates resembling the one in which they once thrived. The three most colossal creatures within that tropical biosphere hold the key to a drug that will bring miraculous life-saving benefits to humankind.

Academy Award® nominee Johansson plays skilled covert operations expert Zora Bennett, contracted to lead a skilled team on a top-secret mission to secure genetic material from the world’s three most massive dinosaurs. When Zora’s operation intersects with a civilian family whose boating expedition was capsized by marauding aquatic dinos, they all find themselves stranded on an island where they come face-to-face with a sinister, shocking discovery that’s been hidden from the world for decades. 

Ali is Duncan Kincaid, Zora’s most trusted team leader; Emmy nominee and Olivier Award winner Jonathan Bailey (Wicked, Bridgerton) plays paleontologist Dr. Henry Loomis; Emmy nominee Rupert Friend (Homeland, Obi-Wan Kenobi) appears as Big Pharma representative Martin Krebs and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo (The Lincoln Lawyer, Murder on the Orient Express) plays Reuben Delgado, the father of the shipwrecked civilian family. 

The cast includes Luna Blaise (Manifest), David Iacono (The Summer I Turned Pretty) and Audrina Miranda (Lopez vs. Lopez) as Reuben’s family. The film also features, as members of Zora and Krebs’ crews, Philippine Velge (Station Eleven), Bechir Sylvain (BMF) and Ed Skrein (Deadpool). 
 
Jurassic World Rebirth is directed by BAFTA winner Edwards from a script by Koepp (War of the Worlds), based on characters created by Michael Crichton. The film is produced by Oscar® nominee Frank Marshall and Patrick Crowley, both longtime Jurassic franchise producers and of this summer’s blockbuster, Twisters. The film is executive produced by Steven Spielberg, Denis L. Stewart and Jim Spencer.

snippet.title: কৃষ্ণনগরে বন্যা | Gopal Bhar | Episode - 1154
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

The people of Krishnanagar are worried as continuous rainfall leads to flooding in the kingdom. Will Gopal come up with a solution in time?

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপালভাঁড়
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language: Bengali
Episode No: 1154

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

Click to watch all the episodes of Gopal Bhar -
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcASj1d8U8PvhnbuO58CfvdkLU

snippet.title: War 2 Teaser Review ⋮ Generic AF
snippet.description:
The War 2 teaser suggests a high-octane action movie with Hrithik Roshan's Kabir being challenged by Jr. NTR, featuring numerous action sequences and a global scale. However, the review notes excessive green screen usage, noticeable CGI, and the absence of a standout "money shot," leading to disappointment compared to expectations set by previous Spy Universe films and Brahmastra. #War2 #PJExplained #thePJ

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Tiffin கடை வச்சிருக்கீங்களா, புது Recipe வேணுமா? Try Pottu Kadalai Kuzhambu | Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
From the bustling kitchens of culinary innovation to the humble hearths of traditional Tamil Nadu, Chef Deena, a connoisseur of authentic flavors, recently found himself captivated. He wasn't just observing; he was witnessing a culinary legacy unfold as the esteemed Mrs. Kavithamani of Thothathu Virundhu, Erode, graciously demonstrated the secrets behind her renowned Pottu Kadalai Kuzhambu.

Thottathu Virunthu,
Mr. Sivanantham & Mrs. Kavithamani Sivanantham
Contact :  9842742126  /9842651113
Thindal - Villarasampatty Rd, near Sree Lakshmi Duraisamy Mahal, 
Villarasampatti, Erode, Tamil Nadu 638012 

Pottu Kadalai Kuzhambu
Fried Gram - 1 Cup 
Tomato - 10 Nos.
Onion - 6 Nos.
Green Chilli - 10 Nos. 
Mustard - For Tempering 
Salt - To Taste
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 Tsp 
Garam Masala - 1/4 Tsp 
Sambar Powder - 1 & 1/2 Tsp 
Groundnut Oil - For Tempering


My Amazon Store { My Picks and Recommended Product }
https://www.amazon.in/shop/chefdeenaskitchen

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.

snippet.title: Google I/O 2025 keynote in 32 minutes
snippet.description:
Google just wrapped up its big keynote at I/O 2025. As expected, it was full of AI-related announcements, ranging from updates across Google’s image and video generation models to new features in Search and Gmail. We got a look at Project Astra’s latest prototype that will complete tasks on your behalf, Gemini 2.5 Pro updates, a new AI filmmaking app called Flow, Project Starline is now Google Beam. Plus, a look at Xreal’s new Project Aura prototype. Here’s everything you missed.

0:00 Intro
0:10 Ironwood
0:26 Google Beam/Project Starline
1:06 Speech Translation in Google Meet
1:55 Project Astra/Gemini Live Demo
2:34 Project Mariner
3:12 Gemini is MCP Compatible
3:25 Agent Mode
4:11 Personal context
4:29 Personalized Smart Replies
5:28 Gemini 2.5 Flash
5:51 Text-to-speech updates
6:45 Security updates and Thought Summaries
7:13 Thinking Budgets
7:30 Gemini 2.5 Flash coding Demo
8:38 Jules coding assistant
8:59 Gemini Diffusion
9:30 Gemini 2.5 Pro Deep Think
10:11 Gemini 2.5 and Project Astra demo
10:55 Scientific AI research apps
11:40 AI Mode in Google Search
12:45 Deep Search and demo
13:57 Search Live
14:11 Visual shopping virtual try-on clothes demo
14:47 Agentic checkout
15:28 Gemini Live demo
16:00 Deep research

18:00 Veo 3

19:30 synthID

23:30 Gemini is everywhere

29:54 Live translation on Android XR

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4403: Trip Ki Taiyyari
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal gears up for his upcoming trip to the Himalayas, and the colony members also express interest. At the same time, he carefully explains to Bapuji how to handle the shop while he's away. Will Bapuji manage smoothly?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4403 | 21 May 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: TRUMP v2.0 | Standup Comedy by Rahul Dua | 2025
snippet.description:
Move over IPL 2.0, here is Trump 2.0.
I travelled to USA and Canada in Feb-Mar 2025 for my standup comedy tour with my new special (btw, India tour is on and I am coming to Australia and New Zealand, so you can get the tickets here: https://linktr.ee/therahulduatour).
This video has jokes about my time and my observations there, based on true events: USA vs Canada, Trump and Elon Musk, missed flights, the tip culture and more. Wrote, rehearsed and recorded all within a month of travel, so pls give it a watch and let me know you favourite joke in the comments below. 
Pls drop a like, it really helps the video. and share it with your friends and family members who are in USA or are planning to visit.

snippet.title: नौकरी गयी तेल लेने, ज्यादा बक-बक की, तो यही पटक कर रख दूंगा - Sanjay Kapoor - Johnny Lever Comedy
snippet.description:
Watch Comedy Scene Of Kader Khan and Johnny Lever From Movie " Sirf Tum "

Get ready for a hilarious rollercoaster with Sirf Tum! Watch as Kader Khan's comic genius and Johnny Lever's impeccable timing combine with Sanjay Kapoor's charm in this laugh-out-loud comedy. From side-splitting mishaps to laughable misunderstandings, this film is packed with moments that will keep you in splits. Whether it’s Kader Khan's comic wisdom or Johnny Lever's laugh-inducing antics, Sirf Tum guarantees endless fun and laughter!"

"Sirf Tum में हंसी की बौछार का आनंद लें! देखिए कैसे कादर खान की हास्य प्रतिभा और जॉनी लीवर का अद्वितीय समय साथ मिलकर संजय कपूर के आकर्षण के साथ हंसते-हंसते लोटपोट कर देते हैं। मजेदार गड़बड़ियों से लेकर हंसी-मजाक की भरपूर स्थिति तक, इस फिल्म में ऐसे पल भरे पड़े हैं जो आपको हंसते-हंसते गिरा देंगे। चाहे कादर खान की हास्य बुद्धिमत्ता हो या जॉनी लीवर की हंसी-मजाक की हरकतें, Sirf Tum हंसी और आनंद की गारंटी है!"

Movie: Sirf Tum (1999)

Cast: Kader Khan, Johnny Lever, Sanjay Kapoor, Priya Gill, Sushmita Sen, Jackie Shroff, Mohnish Behl

Music: Nadeem-Shravan

Director: Agathiyan

Producer: Boney Kapoor

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
